Installation:
=============

        1.  Make a backup of the original NOTEBOOK.S and NOTEBOOK.MAC files
            BEFORE you install the new updated source and macro files.

        2.  Once you have made a backup, unzip NOTEBOOK.S in the ME\SRC
            directory and the NOTEBOOK.MAC in the ME\MAC directory. For
            instance, ME resides on my C: drive in the directory ME.  I
            would then issue the following at the DOS prompt:

            PKUNZIP newnotbk notebook.s C:\ME\SRC

                         THEN...

            PKUNZIP newnotbk notebook.mac C:\ME\MAC

        3.  Then just run Multi-Edit and bring up the notebook.
            There is no need for any data conversion as I didn't change
            the notebook record layout at all.
